reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lots of items to manage all your cables but..
reviews.reviewText: Lots of items to manage your cable systems, but I found many of them to be utterly useless. The velcro long strips that you can tie around the items. They don't hold very well and the velcro's not that strong. The mesh cable ties for the best part of it and I used every single one of them, the black sticky plugs. You can stick on sides of furniture or desks. Throws work really well and the other black ones. I used a couple of those but all of the velcro ones to me were utterly useless. I used a couple of them and some of them kept coming undone but the hard plastic ones and the ones with the hard plastic and the adhesive backings and the mesh black tubes. That's the only way I can describe them. Those were excellent and they also give you several other pieces to use but some of them were way too small for some of my needs. I may use some of the others later and it is a good value, but I think they should have given you more of the black mesh tubes and a lot less of the velcro strips because the velcro strips didn't work that well again. Otherwise for $15 it wasn't that bad

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An infinite number of possibilities of combinations
reviews.reviewText: I ordered the “ELII 300PCS Cable Management Kit,4 Cable Sleeve 35 Cable Clips with 11Cord Holders, 15+5Roll Cable Organizer Straps and 200 Fastening Cable Ties,20 Cable Zip Tie Mounts” to review and to use for a variety of cable management and fastening needs. I recently added a device to my HVAC compressors and found a mess of wires in the component area. I was able to organize and secure the wires with several items from this kit. I absolutely love the variety of items in this kit. It makes for the perfect solution for many projects with an infinite number of possibilities of combinations to choose from.
